    {
      "id": "d4-ann1-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1.5537154949819296,
      "y": 356.7875756894598,
      "width": 290.4996337890625,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "t_4iDu0NQooEX0ArllvcZ"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b08",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2098533000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2045029624,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772702375335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How does the communication work?\n\nBoth sides send JSON messages like:\n{ command: 'search', payload: { query } }\n\nprovider.ts has a switch/case that routes\neach of 17 commands to the right handler.\nThe handler calls APIs or reads files,\nthen sends a typed response back.\n\nIt's like a mini REST API — but messages\ngo through VS Code, not the internet.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How does the communication work?\n\nBoth sides send JSON messages like:\n{ command: 'search', payload: { query } }\n\nprovider.ts has a switch/case that routes\neach of 17 commands to the right handler.\nThe handler calls APIs or reads files,\nthen sends a typed response back.\n\nIt's like a mini REST API — but messages\ngo through VS Code, not the internet.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "syncedAt": "2026-03-05T09:20:07.452Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-03-05T09:20:07.142Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann2-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 335,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
